2. DJANGO REST SETUP

a) Create new virtual envirement

pip install virtualenv
cd VirtualEnv/
virtualenv __NAME_OF_ENVIREMENT__
virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3.4 __NAME_OF_ENVIREMENT__ //adds python3.4 to envirement
source venv/bin/activate

b) Install pip packages
sudo apt-get install python3-dev
pip install -r requirements.txt

c) Setup project
django-admin.py startproject __PROJECT_NAME__
python manage.py startapp __APP_NAME__

d) Database setup
//create localsettings
//setup DATABASES in django_settings

e) lint initiation
pip install pep8